Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1846>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"}],
Text:"THIGUKUU YA MARIA MUTHERU NYINA WA NGAI MWAKA A,B,C"},{Guid:"cRuBMRUJlUq+g6cH5UNNSg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>HWAINI MBERE YA THIGUKUU YA ICIARIRO</s></f></b>"},{
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE</s></f></b>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Isaia. 62:1-5</s></f></b>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s></f></b>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Atĩrĩrĩ, ha ũhoro wa kũrũĩrĩra Sion, ndigatumia kanua, o na kana ndigithĩrie gũtetera Jerusalem,</s></f></b>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>o nginya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ũhoro wakuo wa ũthingu ũkoimbũka ware o ta ũtheri</s></f></b>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>o naguo ũhoro wakuo wa kũhonokania woneke o ta tawa ũrĩa wakanaga mũno.  Nacio ndũrĩrĩ nĩ ikona ũthingu waku, </s></f></b>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>o nao athamaki othe mone riri waku; wee nawe ũcoke gwĩtwo rĩĩtwa rĩngĩ rĩkagwetwo na kanua ka Mwathani.  </s></f></b>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Ningĩ ũgatuĩka ta tanji ya ũthaka ũnyitĩtwo na guoko kwa Mwathani,</s></f></b>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846> na ũhaane ta thũmbĩ ya ũthamaki ĩnyitĩtwo na guoko kwa Ngai waku.  Wee nawe-rĩ, ndũgacoka gwĩtwo Mũtirike, </s></f></b>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>o na kana bũrũri waku wĩtwo Mũkiru Ihooru; na rĩrĩ, ũrĩĩtagwo Hefiziba, </s></f></b>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>o naguo bũrũri waku wĩtagwo Beula; nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani nĩ akenagio nĩwe, </s></f></b>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>o naguo bũrũri waku ũgatuĩka o ta mũhiki ũrĩa ũhikĩtio.  Nĩ gũkorũo o ta ũrĩa mwanake ahikagia mũirĩtu, </s></f></b>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>ũguo noguo aanake aku magakũhikia,</s></f></b>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846> ningĩ o ta ũrĩa mũhikania ekenagĩra nĩ mũhiki wake-rĩ, o ũguo noguo Ngai waku arĩĩkenagĩra nĩwe.</s></f></b>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f></b>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>THABURI 89;3-4,15-16,26,28</s></f></b>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><u><fArial Black><s1846>Icokia:</s></f></u></b><b><fArial Black><s1846>Nġanīrīa hĩndī cīothe, Mwathani mawega makũ.</s></f></b>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Nīī-rī, nindikānīīre na muthurūo wākwa, ndūgatā yākwa Dāudi nī kwīhīta ndīīhītīte </s></f></b>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>ngamīrīkīrīa atīrī mbeū yākū ngumītūūrīa īī numū </s></f></b>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>o ngīnyā tene na tene, ngīākē gītī gīākū kīa ūnēnē gīkīnyagīrīre njīārwā na njīārwā.</s></f></b>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Icokia:Nġanīrīa hĩndī cīothe, Mwathani mawega makũ.</s></f></b>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>wē arītānāgā na kūrī nīī ta ūū; wēw nīwē awa, nōwē mūrungū wākwa, </s></f></b>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>o na ndūmbā yā īhīgā īrīa nyēnē ūhōnōkīō wākwa utūgī wākwa ngūtūrā </s></f></b>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>ndīmūrūmīīrīe kīnyā o tene na tene, 
nakīō kīrīkānīrō gīākū gītūrē kīrī o gīa kwīhōkekā nīwē.</s></f></b>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Icokia:Nġanīrīa hĩndī cīothe, Mwathani mawega makũ.</s></f></b>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>gūkēnārī nī kīrīndī kīrīa kīmenyēte rīūgīrīrīo rīrīa rīa gīkēnō;</s></f></b>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>kīū nīgīthīāgā o na ūtherī wā gīthīīthī gīākū, </s></f></b>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>wēē Jehōvā gītīndāgā gīcānjamūkīte mūthēnyā wōthē nī undū wā rītwā rīū rīākū,</s></f></b>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>na tōndū wā ūthīngu wākū gīgāgītūūgīrīrā.</s></f></b>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Icokia:Nġanīrīa hĩndī cīothe, Mwathani mawega makũ.</s></f></b>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><u><fArial Black><s1846>Gĩthomo gĩa Keri</s></f></u></b><b><fArial Black><s1846>: </s></f></b>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>(Atumwo 13;16-17;22-25)</s></f></b>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Paulo na andũ a thirĩtũ yake magĩkīnya Antiokia nake Paulo agikirugama, na aarikia kumakiria na guoko, akiũgũa atĩrĩ,</s></f></b>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>andu āya a Isiraeli, na inuyui mwītīgagira Ngai tathikirīriai. Ngai wa rurīrī ruru rua Isiraeli </s></f></b>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nīaathurīre maīthe maītu agītūgīrīa andũ a rurīrī ruru </s></f></b>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>hīndī īrīa maātūīre buburī wa Misiri agicoka akīmoīmīa kuo na guoko gwake kwīna uhoti.</s></f></b>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>na aarikia kumwēheria, agīūkīrīa Daudi atūīke muthamaki wāo; </s></f></b>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nīwē Ngai oimburīre uhōrō wake akiūgā atĩrĩ, Ninyonete Daudi, </s></f></b>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>mūrū wa Jesīī, arī mundu urīa ngōrō yākwā yendīre o ngōga, </s></f></b>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>urīa urīkāga maundū mārīa mothe ndīrīendāga mekwo. </s></f></b>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Na rīrī, Ngai nīaarehīthīrīe Āīsirāelī muhonōkīa oīmīte rucīārō-īnī rūa mundu ūcīo, </s></f></b>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>o tā urīa erānīīre, nake nīwē Jesū.</s></f></b>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Ūcīo atānokarī, Johānā nīāmbīrīe kuhunjīrīa andũ ōthe a Isiraeli uhōrō wa atī andũ mērīre gūkū thīrī, </s></f></b>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>akiūgā atĩrĩ, mugūkīgererīa atī nīī ndī ū?</s></f></b>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Nīī tī nīī urīa ugūkā. Nō atīrī, nīharī ugūkā thūta wākwa, urīa nīī itāīgaīne wa kuohorā mikwā yā iratū cīāke.</s></f></b>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcīo ciūgō cīa Mwathānī.</s></f></b>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><u><fArial Black><s1846>Rwĩmbō rwa injĩlĩ</s></f></u></b>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Āllelūia, āllelūia</s></f></b>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Rūcīu urū wa thĩ ūgāthīra, na ūthāmākī wa thĩ agāthānā īgūrū rīītu.</s></f></b>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Āllelūia</s></f></b>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>INJILI: </s></f></b>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>(Mathayo : 25)</s></f></b>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Ühoro wa rūciaro rūria Jesu Kristo,
mūrŭ wa Daudi, mūrũ wa Iburahımu, oimire.
Iburahimu niwe waciarire Isaaka,</s></f></b>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Isaaka agiciara Jakubu; nake
Jakubu agiciara Juda o na ariūũ a ithe; </s></f></b>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Juda agiciara Perezu na Zera,
na nyina wao aari Tamaru; </s></f></b>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Perezu agiciara Hezironi; nake Hezi-roni agīciara Ramu, </s></f></b>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Ramu agīciara Aminadabu; nake Aminadabu
agiciara Nahashonı ; nake Nahashoni agiciara Salimoni; </s></f></b>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Salimoni agiciara Boazu, na nyina aari Rahabu; nake Boazu agiciara Obedi, na nyina aari Ruthu; </s></f></b>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>näke Obedi agiciara Jesii; nake Jesii agīciara Daudi,
üria wari mūthamaki.</s></f></b>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Nake Daudi agiciara Solomoni, na nyina aari mūtumia üria wari o mbere wa Uria; ' </s></f></b>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Solomoni agiciara Rehoboamu; nake Rehoboamu agi-ciara Abija; </s></f></b>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Abija agiciara Asa; nake Asa agiciara Jehoshafatu;
nake Jehoshafatu agiciara Joramu;</s></f></b>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Joramu agīciara Uzia; nake Uzia agiciara Jothamu; nake Jothamu agiciara Ahazu; </s></f></b>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Ahazu agiciara Hezekia; nake Hezekia agiciara Manase; </s></f></b>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Manase agīciara Amoni; nake Amoni agiciara Josia; </s></f></b>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Josia agiciara Jekonia na ariû a ithe,
hindi iria andū maatahirūo magitwarūo Babuloni.</s></f></b>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>O na andū maąrīkia gūtahwo magītwarūo kūu Babuloni, Jekonia</s></f></b>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>ūcio agiciara Shealitieli; nake Shealitieli agiciara Zerubabeli; </s></f></b>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Zerubabeli agiciara Abihudu; nake Abihudu agiciara Eliakimi; </s></f></b>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Eliakimi agīciara Azoro; nake Azoro agiciara Zadoku, </s></f></b>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Zadoku agiciara Akimi, nake Akimi agiciara Eliudu,</s></f></b>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Eliudu agiciara Eleazaru; nake Eleazaru agiciara Mathani;</s></f></b>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Mathani agiciara Jakubu; nake Jakubu agiciara Jusufu,</s></f></b>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>uria wari muthuri wa mariamu, uria waciarire Jesu, uria witagwo Kristo</s></f></b>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Noguo njiaro ciothe gwata Iburahimu kinya Daudi, ni ikūmi nainya;</s></f></b>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846> 
ningi gwata Daudi kinya andũ maatahwo magītwarūo Babiloni,</s></f></b>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>ni njiaro ikūmi na inya; ria ningi gwata andû maatahwo magitwarüo kūu</s></f></b>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Babiloni, kinya Kristo, ni njiaro ikümi na inya.</s></f></b>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Ningi gwata Daudi kinya andu maatahwo magitwaro Babiloni, ni njiaro ikumi na inya;</s></f></b>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>na ningi gwata andu maatahwo magitwaro
kuu Babiloni, kinya Kristo, ni njiaro ikumi na inya</s></f></b>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Riu-ri, gūcıarūo kwa Jesu Krısto gwatarii ūu' nyina Mariamu orio ni Jusufu, </s></f></b>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>matanonana, akionwo ar</s></f></b><b><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f></b><b><fArial Black><s1846> na ihu rĩa Roho Mãtheru. </s></f></b>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Nake mūthuriwe Jusufu, tondū aari mũndū mūthingu, na ndendaga gūcono-rithia</s></f></b>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846> 
müiritu ücio küri andű, akienda atigane nake na hitho.Na hindi Iria eciragia maündū macio, </s></f></b>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>atiriri, müraika wa Mwathanı akimuumirira kiroto-ini, akimwira atiri, Jusufu, mũrũ wa Daudi, </s></f></b>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>ndūgetigire kühikia Mariamu atuike mūtumia waku, tondū-ri, </s></f></b>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>ihu riu ari narīo ni ria Roho Mütheru. Nake niagaciara kahii, nako niügagatua JESU, </s></f></b>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>ni ündũ niwe ükahonokia andū ake mehia-ini mao. </s></f></b>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Na riri, maūndū macio mekirūo ni getha ciugo iria cioigirüo ni Mwathari na kanua ka műnabii ikinye, riria oigire atiri:</s></f></b>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Onei, müiritu niakagīa ihu, na aciare kalhil, Nako gatuwo Imanueli;</s></f></b>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>üguo naguo ügitaürűo, nĩ kuuga, Ngai hamwe na ithui. </s></f></b>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>Nake Jusufu agiükira toro, agīika o ta üria müraika wa Mwathani aamwathire, akihikia </s></f></b>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<s1076></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>mütumia wake, kinya na ndaigana kümūmenya aaciara kahii; agigatua
JESU.</s></f></b>"}],
Text:"HWAINI MBERE YA THIGUKUU YA ICIARIRO"},{Guid:"t7RxNF5aiE24tbtVIXavrA",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Danieli 7:13-14</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KĨRORI DANIELI: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngĩcoka ngĩkĩona maũndũ mangĩ na </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>cioneki cia ũtukũ, na atĩrĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>He mũndũ wahaanaga  ta mũrũ wa mũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wokire na matũ ma igũrũ,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> nake agĩkinya harĩ Ũrĩa-ũtũire-ho-kuuma-o-tene,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na agĩtwaratwarũo hakuhĩ nake.  </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake agĩkĩheo wathani, na riri, o na ũthamaki, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩgetha andũ a nduka ciothe,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na a ndũrĩrĩ  ciothe, na a mĩario yothe, mamũtungatagĩre. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naguo wathani ũcio wake nĩ wa mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ndũgathira o rĩ, o rĩ.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naguo ũthamaki ũcio wake ndũkonũhĩka o  na atĩa.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                         Thaburi 93:1ab;1c-2;5</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ũroka ũnene waku wa ũtheri</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ hĩndĩ Mwathani agwatĩte gũthamaka; nĩ ũnene ehumbĩte; </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwĩhumba, Mwathani nĩ ehumbĩte hinya, akawĩoha ta ndoho.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ũroka ũnene waku wa ũtheri</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ĩĩ-ni, thĩ nĩ kũrũmio ĩrũmĩtio, ũndũ ĩtangĩenyenyeka.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Gĩtĩ gĩaku kĩa ũnene gĩtũire gĩĩ kĩrũmu kuuma o tene na tene, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wee-rĩ, ũtũire o ho gwata mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ũroka ũnene waku wa ũtheri</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maũira maku, Mwathani, nĩ mehokeku o mũno, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũtheru ũgũtũũra wagĩrĩtie nyũmba yaku, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>matukũ matarĩ mũthia.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ũroka ũnene waku wa ũtheri</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                        Kũguũrĩrio 1:5-8</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KŨGUŨRĨRIO</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu Kristũ, mũira ũrĩa mwĩhokeku, o we irigithathi rĩa arĩa akuũ, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nowe mwathi wa athamaki a thĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>we ũcio ũtwenda, na watuohorire na thakame </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yake tuume mehia-inĩ maitũ, na agĩtũtua kĩrĩndĩ kĩa mũthamaki,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> tũtuĩke athĩnjĩri Ngai wake, o we Ithe-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũgoocwo na Mwathani arogĩaga kũrĩ we nginya tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ gũtuĩke guo.  Atĩrĩrĩi, nĩ gũũka egũũka na matu, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na gũtirĩ riitho rĩtakamuona, o na arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maamũthecire o nao mamuone; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ndũrĩrĩ ciothe cia thĩ nĩ gũcakaya nĩ ũndũ wake.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Noguo gũgatuĩka, Nĩ gũtuĩke guo.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ niĩ Alfa o na Omega, nĩguo Mwathani Ngai ekuuga, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa ũrĩ ho, na nowe warĩ ho, na nowe ũgũũka, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o we Mwene-Hinya-Wothe.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Mark 11,10</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ ũrĩa ũgũũka na rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani! </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ ũthamakĩ ũrĩa ũgũũka.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                        John 18:33b-37</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo Pilato akĩũria Yesu: Wee nĩwe </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mũthamaki wa Ayahudi? Nake Yesu agĩcokia atĩrĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũkũũria ũguo wĩrĩtwo nĩ ngoro yaku mwene, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kana nĩ andũ angĩ makwĩrire ũhoro wakwa? </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Pilato agĩcokia atĩrĩ: Kaĩ ndĩ mũyahudi 
niĩ? </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Anga ti rũrĩrĩ rũanyu na athacerdoti arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>anene maakũneana kũrĩ niĩ; nĩ atĩa wĩkĩte? </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu agĩcokia atĩrĩrĩ: Ũthamaki wakwa ti </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wana gũkũ thĩ; ũthamaki wakwa ũngĩrĩ wa gũkũ thĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>andũ akwa mangĩrĩ kũruta mbaara, ndikaneo </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ayahudi; no rĩrĩ, ũrĩa kũrĩ, ũthamaki wakwa ti wana gũkũ.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tondũ ũcio Pilato  akĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Anga ũkĩrĩ o mũthamaki, wee? </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu agĩcokia atĩrĩrĩ: wee nĩ woiga, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amu ndĩ mũthamaki.  Nĩkĩo ndaciarirũo, na </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩkĩo njũkĩte gũkũ thĩ, atĩ nduĩke  mũira wa ũhoro-ũrĩa-wa-ma.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũhoro-ũrĩa-wa-ma-rĩ, mũndũ o wothe waguo </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ aiguaga mũgambo wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],
Text:"THIGUKUU YA MWATHANI WITU YESU KRISTU MUTHAMAKI"},{Guid:"bMfohIvqbUmhjdsAV4+uDw",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s2769><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>THIGUKUU YA EPIPHANIA </k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
</s></f><fArial Black><s2769><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Isaia 60:1-6</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Atĩrĩrĩ, ũkĩra ũikare ũcangararĩte, nĩ ũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũtheri wa gũgũtherera nĩ mũũku, naguo riri </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa Mwathani ũkũratha ta riũa ũkwarĩre. Tondũ rĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nduma nĩ ikaiyũra thĩ, nayo nduma ndumanu ĩhumbĩre ndũrĩrĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>no wee-rĩ Mwathani nĩ kwara agakwarĩra, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o naguo riri wake wonagwo ũkwarĩire. Nacio ndũrĩrĩ </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>igokokaga harĩ ũtheri waku,
o nao athamaki mokokage </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makinye kũrĩa ũcangararĩte ta riũa rĩkĩratha. Atĩrĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>inamũra maitho maku wĩhũgũre na mĩena yothe wĩonere ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>andũ mecokanĩrĩirie, magoka harĩ wee; arĩũ aku makoima </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũndũ kũraya mũno, o nao airĩtu aku moke makuuĩtwo na ngoi.  </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo nĩ ũkona wega,
warĩrio ũtheri, o nayo ngoro </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yaku nĩ ĩgacamjamũka  o na ĩigue wega nĩ ũrĩa ĩmakũkĩte, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tondũ indo ciothe iria ikuuagwo ikagerio igũrũ rĩa </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>iria rĩrĩa inene, o ta ũrĩa ciingĩhĩte, nĩ ikerekerio harĩ </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wee, o naguo ũtonga wa ndũrĩrĩ ũrehwo harĩ wee. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngamĩra nyingĩ cia rũgendo nĩ ikaiyũra gwaku, o nacio njaũ cia ngamĩra cia </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Madiana, o na Efa, nacio ciothe ikorũo ciumĩte Saba.  Nacio thahabu na 
ũbani </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩcio ikarehe, o na iheanage ũhoro wa ũrĩa Mwathani akumagio.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
</s></f><fArial Black><s2769><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Thaburi 72: 1;7-8;10-11;12-13</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
</s></f><fArial Black><s2769><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Ndũrĩrĩ ciothe nĩ igagũturĩria maru, wee Mwathani </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ĩ Ngai, he mũthamaki mĩtuĩre yaku, o we mũriũ </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa mũthamaki-rĩ, ũkĩmũhe ũthingu waku.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
</s></f><fArial Black><s2769><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Ndũrĩrĩ ciothe nĩ igagũturĩria maru, wee Mwathani </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Matukũ make ũrĩa mũthingu nĩ kũhamba arĩhambaga, na gũtũũre na thayũ mũingĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nginya  o hingo mweri ũkarindũka.
Nĩ agĩe na watho kuuma </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>iria-inĩ rĩmwe o nginya rĩrĩa rĩngĩ, na kuuma rũũĩ-inĩ o nginya ituri cia thĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
</s></f><fArial Black><s2769><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Ndũrĩrĩ ciothe nĩ igagũturĩria maru, wee Mwathani </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Athamaki a Tarsis na mabũrũri ma iria-inĩ, nĩ mamũrutagĩre maruta; athamaki </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>a Sheba na a Saba o nao nĩ mamũtegagĩre matega.Ĩĩ-ni, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>athamaki othe marokĩmũgũĩra thĩ atungatagĩrũo nĩ ndũrĩrĩ ciothe.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
</s></f><fArial Black><s2769><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Ndũrĩrĩ ciothe nĩ igagũturĩria maru, wee Mwathani </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ ũndũ mũndũ mũkĩa aakaya, we nĩ arĩmũteithũraga, gwata ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũthĩnĩki, ũtakĩrĩ na wa kũmũteithia.
Ũcio ũtarĩ na hinya, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o ũcio mwagi-rĩ, nĩ arĩmũiguagĩra tha; andũ acio akĩa, akĩhonokie mĩoyo yao.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
</s></f><fArial Black><s2769><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Ndũrĩrĩ ciothe nĩ igagũturĩria maru, wee Mwathani </k></c></s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
</s></f><fArial Black><s2769><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Aefeso 3:2-3,5-6</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A EFESO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a ithe witũ, mũngĩgĩkorũo nĩ mũiguĩte ũhoro wa ũramati </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa wega wa Ngai ũrĩa heetwo nĩ ũndũ wanyu, na </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũgakorũo nĩ mũiguĩte ũrĩa ndamenyithirio ũhoro </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa wa hitho nĩ ũndũ wa kũguũrĩrio nĩ Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o ta ũrĩa ndamwandĩkĩire o kabere na ciugo itarĩ nyingĩ.  </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O ũcio ũtonirio ciana cia kĩrĩndĩ hĩndĩ ya njiaro ingĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ta ũrĩa rĩu ũrĩkĩtie kũguũrĩrio atũmwo ake atheru o na </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>anabii nĩ muoyo. Naguo nĩ ũyũ, atĩ andũ a ndũrĩrĩ nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>matuĩkĩte agai hamwe na ithuĩ na ningĩ a mwĩrĩ 
ũmwe na ithuĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>magagĩtuĩka a ngwatanĩro ĩmwe na ithuĩ ũhoro-inĩ wa </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kĩĩranĩro kĩrĩa kĩarehirũo nĩ Kristũ Yesu na ũndũ wa </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũhunjanĩria ũhoro-ũrĩa mwega.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s2769><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Mathayo2,2 </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Alleluya. Alleluya</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s2769><kFFD80000>.</k></s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769><kFFD80000>Nĩ twonire njata yake kũrĩa </k></s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769><kFFD80000>irathĩro-inĩ na nĩ tũũkĩte tũmũturĩrie ndu tũgooce Mwathani. </k></s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Alleluia</k></c></s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s2769><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Mathayo 2:1-12</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MATHAYO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na rĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa  Yesu aciarĩirũo Bethlehemu, itũũra rĩa Judea,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>matukũ ma mũthamaki wetagwo Herode, gũgĩũka andũ ogĩ </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>a njata Jerusalem, moimire kũrĩa irathĩro-inĩ, makĩũria atĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>“Ũrĩa ũciarĩtwo e mũthamaki wa Ayahudi, arĩ ha?”</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tondũ nĩ twonire njata yake kũrĩa irathĩro-inĩ, na nĩ tũũkĩte </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tũmuturirĩe ndu tũmũgooce.  Na rĩrĩa Herode, ũcio ,mũthamaki, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aaiguire ũhoro ũcio akĩĩgua ũũru, we mwene o na Jerusalem </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>guothe hamwe nake. Agĩkĩũngania athĩnjĩri Ngai arĩa anene othe na </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aandĩki-marũa a kĩrĩndĩ, akĩmoria harĩa Kristũ agaciarĩrũo. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nao makĩmwĩra, Nĩ Bethlehem, itũũra rĩa Judea, tondũ nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwandĩkĩtwo nĩ mũrathi ũũ: Nawe Bethlehem,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o kũu bũrũri wa Judea, tiwe ũrĩa mũnyinyi  mũno wa aathani a Juda: </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tondũ rĩ, nĩ kũrĩ wee gũkoima ũrĩa agaathanaga, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o ũrĩa ũkarĩithagia andũ akwa Israeli”. Hĩndĩ ĩo Herode agĩĩta andũ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>acio ogĩ a njata na hitho, 
agĩtuĩria wega kũrĩ o hĩndĩ ĩrĩa njata </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yonekire. Akĩmatũma Bethlehem, akĩmera, thiĩi, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũgatuĩrie wega ũhoro wa gakenge kau, na mwakona, cokai mũhe </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũhoro, nĩ getha na niĩ thiĩ ngagaturĩrie ndu ndĩkagooce. Nao </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maaigua ũrĩa mũthamaki ũcio aamerire,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> magĩĩthiĩra; na rĩrĩ, njata ĩrĩa monire o kũrĩa irathĩro-inĩ ĩkamathiĩ mbere, o nginya ĩkĩrũgama igũrũ rĩa harĩa gakenge kau kaarĩ</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nao mona njata ĩo, magĩkena gĩkeno kĩnene mũno. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Magĩtonya nyũmba, makĩona gakenge karĩ na nyina Maria, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Makĩĩgũithia thĩ, magĩkagooca.  Makĩohora indo ciao cia goro na cio ciarĩ thahabu, ũbani na manemane. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na tondũ wa gũkanio nĩ Ngai na kĩroto, atĩ matigacokere kũrĩ Herode, magĩcoka bũrũri wao na njĩra ĩngĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"Candle.jpg",Luminosity:-45}},
Text:"THIGUKUU YA EPIPHANIA MWAKA A,B,C"},{Guid:"pglKvSTUrkmcItfzrx1vqA",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Luminosity:-50}},
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>SHEREHE YA BIKIRA MARIA, MAMA WA MUNGU</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"InShot_20251230_132513762.jpg",BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Hesabu 6;22-27</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Hesabu</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana alimwambia Musa: “Mwambie Haruni na wanawe:</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hivi ndivyo mtakavyowabariki wana wa Israeli.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mtawaambia:
Bwana akubariki na kukulinda!</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akuangazie uso wake,na kukufadhili!</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akuelekezee uso wake na kukuletea amani!</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Waliweke hivyo jina langu juu ya wana wa Israeli,
nami nitawabariki.\"</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Zaburi 67:2-3.5, 6 na 8 (K. 2a</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mungu na aturehemu na kutubariki.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu na aturehemu na kutubariki,
atuangazie uso wake.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Njia yake itambulike duniani,
na wokovu wake katika mataifa yote. K.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mungu na aturehemu na kutubariki.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mataifa na wafurahi na kushangilia,
kwa kuwa unawatawala kwa haki,
na kuwaongoza mataifa ya dunia. K.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mungu na aturehemu na kutubariki.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Watu na wakutukuze, ee Mungu,
watu wote na wakutukuze!</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu atatubariki sisi,
na miisho yote ya dunia itamcha Mungu wetu. K.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mungu na aturehemu na kutubariki.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Wagalatia 4:4-7</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wagalatia</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Wakati ulipowadia, Mungu alimtuma Mwana wake</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alivezaliwa na mwanamke, aliyezaliwa chini ya sheria, ili awakomboe</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>waliokuwa chini ya sheria, tuweze kufanywa wana.
Basi, kwa kuwa ninyi mu wana, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu amemtuma Roho wa Mwana
wake mioyoni mwenu aliaye, “Abba, Baba.\" </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa hiyo wewe si mtumwa tena, baliu mwana, na ukiwa mwana, u pia mrithi kwa Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Waebranía 1:1-2</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>K. Aleluya. W. Aleluya.
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>K. Mara nyingi na kwa namna nyingi
Mungu alisema na mababu zetu kwa njia ya manabii.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku hizi za mwisho amesema na sisi kwa njia ya Mwana.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>W. Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Luka 2:16-21</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati huo: [Wachungaji] walienda kwa haraka Bethlehemu.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakamkuta Maria na Yosefu, na mtoto mchanga amelala horin.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Walipomwona, walieleza habari waliyoambiwa juu ya mtoto huyu. </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wote waliosikia wakayastaajabia maneno waliyoambiwa na wachungaji. </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naye Maria akatunza mambo hayo yote akiyavwaza
moyoni mwake. </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wachungaji wakarudi kwao wakimtukuza na
kumsifu</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu kwa yote waliyoyasikia na kuyaona,
walivyoambiwa.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Zilipotimia siku nane, ndio wakati wa kumtahiri mtoto, aliitwa jina lake Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kama alivyoitwa na malaika kabla ya kutungwa mimba.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"InShot_20251230_132513762.jpg"}},
Text:"SHEREHE YA BIKIRA MARIA MAMA WA MUNGU"},{Guid:"uT5b8cdYSUKbPJvweiCvtg",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"Candle.jpg"}},
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>KUTOKEA KWAKE BWANA YESU (EPIFANIA)</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA	
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Isaya 60: I-6</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Isaya</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amka! Uangaze, ewe Yerusalemu, kwa kuwa nuru yako imekuja, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao utukufu wa Bwana umekaa juu yako. Tazama, giza limeifunika dunia, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na giza kuu limeyafunika mataifa, lakini juu yako Bwana atatokea, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao utukufu wake utaonekana juu yako. Mataifa watatembea katika </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwanga wako, nao wafalme katika weupe wa alfajiri yako.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inua macho, utazame pande zote; wote wamekusanyika, wanakujia </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wana wako watakuja toka mbali, binti zako wanabebwa kiunoni.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa kuona hayo, utatiwa nuru, moyo wako utapendezwa nayo na kuona raha; </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maana mali ya nchi za ng'ambo ya bahari zitakujia, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na utajiri wa mataifa utakujia kwa wingi.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Makundi ya ngamia watakufunika, ngamia vijana wa Midiani na Efa.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Watu wa Sheba watakuja, wakileta dhahabu na ubani, na kutangaza sifa za Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Zaburi 72: 7-8, 10-11. 12-13</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mataifa yote ya ulimwengu watakusujudia, ee Bwana.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee Mungu, umpe mfalme hukumu yako; na mwana wa mfalme haki yako; </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ahukumu taifa lako kwa haki, na wanyonge kwa usawa. </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K: </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mataifa yote ya ulimwengu watakusujudia, ee Bwana.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Katika siku zake haki iendelee, na amani izidi mpaka mwezi ukome.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atawale toka bahari hata bahari, na toka ule mto hata miisho ya dunia. </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mataifa yote ya ulimwengu watakusujudia, ee Bwana.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wafalme wa Tarshishi na visiwa watatoa kodi, </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wafalme wa Sheba na Seba wataleta zawadi.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wafalme wote wa dunia watamwangukia, mataifa yote watamtumikia. </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K: </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mataifa yote ya ulimwengu watakusujudia, ee Bwana.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana atamkomboa maskini mwenye kumlilia, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mnyonge asiye na msaidizi. Atamhurumia na mhitaji, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na anayaokoa maisha ya wahitaji. </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mataifa yote ya ulimwengu watakusujudia, ee Bwana.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Waefeso 3:2-3a,5,6</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Waefeso</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu:Nadhani mmesikia jinsi Mungu alivyonikabidhi neema </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya kuwasaidia ninyi, yaani kwa kunifunulia ujuzi wa fumbo, kwa wazee wa zamani</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>fumbo hilo halikujulikana kama lilivyofunuliwa sasa na Roho kwa mitume</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na manabii wake watakatifu.
Maana sasa watu wa Mataifa hurithi pamoja </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nasi pia ni viungo vya mwili mmoja nasi, na wanashiriki </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ahadi moja nasi katika Kristu Yesu kwa njia ya Injili.</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Mathayo 2; 2</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya. Aleluya. </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tuliona nyota yake mashariki. </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tumekuja kumwabudu Bwana. </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Mathayo 2:1-12</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Mathayo</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu alipozaliwa Bethlehemu wa Yudea wakati wa mfalme Herode, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tazama, mamajusi wa mashariki walifika Yerusalemu, wakisema, </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Yuko wapi aliyezaliwa 
mfalme wa Wayahudi? </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana tuliona nyota yake mashariki. Tumekuja kumwabudu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mfalme Herode aliposikia hayo, alihangaika sana, na Yerusalemu yote pamoja naye. </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akawakusanya makuhani wakuna Waandishi wote wa watu, </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akawauliza mahali pa kuzaliwa Kristu. Nao wakamwambia, \"Bethlehemu ya Yudea, </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana nabii ameandikwa hivi: 'Ee Bethlehemu, </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika nchi ya Yuda, huwi kamwe mji wa mwisho </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kati ya miji mikubwa ya Yuda, kwa maana kwako </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atatokea kiongozi 
atakayewachunga watu wangu Israeli. \"</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hapo Herode akawaita 
mamajusi kwa faragha, </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akawahoji kuhusu wakati 
nyota ile ilipotokea. </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akawatuma waende Bethlehemu akisema, </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Nendeni mkapeleleze kwa bidii habari za mtoto. </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mkimkuta, nipasheni habari, ili nami pia niende nikamwabudu.\" </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Walimsikiliza mfalme, wakaenda. Na tazama, nyota </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ile waliyoiona katika nchi ya mashariki ikawatangulia tena, </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hata ilipofika ikasimama juu ya mahali alipokuwapo mtoto. </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Walipoiona tena nyota, 
walifurahi kwa furaha kubwa sana. </s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakaingia nyumbani, 
wakamwona mtoto pamoja na Maria mama yake. </s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakaanguka, wakamwabudu. 
Wakafungua hazina zao, </s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakamtolea zawadi za dhahabu, ubani na manemane. </s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakiisha kuonywa katika 
ndoto wasimrudie Herode, </s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakarudi nchini kwao kwa njia nyingine.</s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],VersionDate:"20260101113303",Style:{Background:{Image:"Candle.jpg",Luminosity:-45}},
Text:"KUTOKEA KWAKE BWANA YESU (EPIFANIA)
"},{Guid:"81FUHKQuSkWz2J72LLuohg",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1384>Gikuyu
</s></f></u><fArial Black><s1384>V/.Niĩ ndĩ ndungata ya Mwathani;
R/.Nĩ njīkwo ta ürīa woiga</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1384>Kiswahili
</s></f></u><fArial Black><s1384>V).Mimi ni mtumishi wa Bwana;
R).Nitendewe ulivyonena</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1384>English
</s></f></u><fArial Black><s1384>V).I am the handmaid of the Lord
R/.Let it be done to me according to your word</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF000000"}}},
Text:"MWAKA WA MARIA"}],IsCompressed:0,Guid:"QFLHBwenIEerhytaBzLhrw",VersionDate:"20260101113303",
Text:"THIGUKUU CIA KANITHA AND KISWAHILI"}